text: Mukhya Mantri Yuva Swarozgar Yojana or MMYSY is a government of Madhya Pradesh scheme under which the State Government will give bank guarantee and loan subsidy to promote entrepreneurship.Mukhya Mantri Yuva Swarozgar Yojna Scheme for Madhya PradeshMP: Mukhyamantri Yuva Swarozgar Yojana from April 1 ==References== Category:Government schemes in Madhya Pradesh Category:Entrepreneurship in India
title: Mukhya Mantri Yuva Swarozgar Yojana
